{
  "stem": "25639.10",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at the same time-- oh, actually, she wanted to go to Tucson, Arizona and then visit Los Angeles at the same time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she loved it so much, she decided to move there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so this was just fine with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because while I was in Kansas City, Missouri, I met my husband, who was a law student from Hastings College of Law in San Francisco.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he went home to be with his parents for the summer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "By this time, he had an accounting degree from the University of California.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so he was going to go to-- he was going to law school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he just finished his first year when I met him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I met-- [LAUGHS] my girlfriend Lucy from Paris, France had a birthday.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she invited her girlfriends for her birthday on a Saturday night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, when you are 17, Saturday night is special.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you date and you are almost restricted on the nights when you can go out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we decided to go and honor Lucy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my American girlfriend, [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Signe ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Kaufmann ?] and I, went to Lucy's birthday party.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And but what did she do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Typical of a French girl, of that time I should say, she invited a set of boys of her own.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the meantime, I was lonely for my boyfriend, Eric.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there we danced.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And while we were having a good time in this private home, three young men-- who came to Kansas City, one from Harvard, I think medical school, the other one from a Texas University, he was studying engineering, and Carl, from Hastings studying law.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the three buddies came home for the summer, and what to do on a Saturday night?",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
